  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What can I give my best friend on her birthday?",
  "response": "Choosing a birthday gift for your best friend depends on her interests, your relationship, and your budget. Here are some thoughtful ideas across different categories:\n\n### Personalized Gifts\n- **Custom Jewelry:** A necklace or bracelet with her initials or a special date.\n- **Photo Album/Scrapbook:** Filled with memories of your time together.\n- **Personalized Mug or Tote Bag:** With a special message or design that reflects her personality.\n\n### Experience Gifts\n- **Spa Day:** Treat her to a relaxing day at a local spa.\n- **Concert or Show Tickets:** If she loves music or theater, tickets to see her favorite performer or show.\n- **Cooking or Art Class:** An experience where you can learn something new together.\n\n### Practical Gifts\n- **High-Quality Planner or Journal:** If she's organized or loves to write.\n- **Tech Gadgets:** Like a smart home device or a stylish phone case.\n- **Subscription Box:** Tailored to her interests, such as beauty, books, or gourmet foods.\n\n### Fun and Whimsical Gifts\n- **Board Games or Puzzles:** For a fun night in.\n- **Novelty Items:** Like a funny mug or a quirky piece of decor.\n- **DIY Kit:** Such as a knitting kit or a DIY candle-making set.\n\n### Sentimental Gifts\n- **Handwritten Letter:** Expressing what she means to you.\n- **Memory Jar:** Fill it with notes of favorite moments and why you appreciate her.\n- **Friendship Book:** A book about friendship with a heartfelt inscription from you.\n\n### Budget-Friendly Ideas\n- **Homemade Treats:** Bake her favorite cookies or cake.\n- **Playlist:** Curate a playlist of songs that are meaningful to your friendship.\n- **DIY Crafts:** Create something handmade like a painting or a knit scarf.\n\nThe most important thing is to show that you put thought into the gift. Consider what she enjoys and how you can make her day special. Whether it's a small token or a grand gesture, the sentiment behind it is what truly matters.",
